 The purpose of the Phase 1b portion of this study is to compare the NDV-3A vaccine, the NDV-3 vaccine and the placebo head-to-head in the patient population of interest (women with RVVC) to evaluate safety and immunogenicity.

 The study size for comparing safety and immunogenicity (N=15 per group) is based on the dose comparison design used in study NDV3-001 (clinical trials.

